msgid "News - 16 series"
msgstr "お知らせ - 16系"

msgid "Release 16.05 - 2026-06-08"
msgstr "16.05リリース - 2026-06-08"

msgid "Improvements"
msgstr "改良"

msgid "Added support for MariaDB 10.6.26 in the following OS"
msgstr "以下のOSでMariaDB 10.6.26をサポート"

msgid "AlmaLinux 8, 9"
msgstr ""

msgid "Added support for MariaDB 10.11.17 in the following OS"
msgstr "以下のOSでMariaDB 10.11.17をサポート"

msgid "AlmaLinux 8, 9, 10"
msgstr ""

msgid "Added support for MariaDB 11.4.11 in the following OS"
msgstr "以下のOSでMariaDB 11.4.11をサポート"

msgid "Added support for MariaDB 11.8.7 in the following OS"
msgstr "以下のOSでMariaDB 11.8.7をサポート"

msgid "Added support for MySQL 8.0.46 in the following OS"
msgstr "以下のOSでMySQL 8.0.46をサポート"

msgid "Debian 12"
msgstr ""

msgid "Ubuntu 22.04, 24.04"
msgstr ""

msgid "Added support for MySQL 8.4.9 in the following OS"
msgstr "以下のOSでMySQL 8.4.9をサポート"

msgid "Debian 12, 13"
msgstr ""

msgid "Release 16.01 - 2026-03-30"
msgstr "16.01リリース - 2026-03-30"

msgid "Added support for Percona Server for MySQL 8.0.45-36 in the following OS"
msgstr "以下のOSでPercona Server for MySQL 8.0.45-36をサポート"

msgid "8.0.45-36 is the latest Percona Server for MySQL 8.0 release."
msgstr "8.0.45-36は最新のPercona Server for MySQL 8.0のリリースです。"

msgid "Added support for Percona Server for MySQL 8.4.8-8 in the following OS"
msgstr "以下のOSでPercona Server for MySQL 8.4.8-8をサポート"

msgid "AlmaLinux 9, 10"
msgstr ""

msgid "8.4.8-8 is the latest Percona Server for MySQL 8.4 release."
msgstr "8.4.8-8は最新のPercona Server for MySQL 8.4のリリースです。"

msgid "Added support for MariaDB 11.8.6 on Debian 13"
msgstr "Debian 13でMariaDB 11.8.6をサポートしました。"

msgid "This is the latest MariaDB 11.8 release."
msgstr "11.8.6は最新のMariaDB 11.8のリリースです。"

msgid "Dropped support for `engine \"XXX\"` in CONNECTION for wrapper mode"
msgstr "ラッパーモードで`CONNECTION=engine \"XXX\"`のサポートをやめました。"

msgid "[[MDEV-38530]( https://jira.mariadb.org/browse/MDEV-38530 )][Reported by Roel Van de Paar]"
msgstr "[[MDEV-38530]( https://jira.mariadb.org/browse/MDEV-38530 )][Roel Van de Paarさんの報告]"

msgid "Mroonga accepted `engine \"XXX\"` for wrapper mode not only in `COMMENT` but also in `CONNECTION`. However, this behavior was neither documented nor tested, so support for it has been removed."
msgstr "Mroongaのラッパーモードで`CONNECTION=engine \"XXX\"`という書き方もできるようになっていますが、これについてドキュメントもテストも存在しないため、この機能を削除しました。"

msgid "Fixes"
msgstr "修正"

msgid "Fixed a crash bug that occurred when `mroonga_log_file` was set `NULL` or an empty string"
msgstr "`mroonga_log_file`に`NULL`または、空の文字列を設定するとMroongaがクラッシュする問題を修正しました。"

msgid "[[GH-1069]( https://github.com/mroonga/mroonga/pull/1069 )][Patched by Hadeer Ramadan]"
msgstr "[[GH-1069]( https://github.com/mroonga/mroonga/pull/1069 )][Hadeer Ramadanさんがパッチ提供]"

msgid "Setting `NULL` or an empty string as shown below caused a `SIGSEGV`."
msgstr "以下のように`NULL`または、空の文字列を設定すると、`SIGSEGV`が発生します。"

msgid "Thanks"
msgstr "感謝"

